In this edition of Still T.R.E.(nding), Jack and Miles discuss an armed man threatening to kill Brett Kavanaugh, Steve Scalise compares 9/11 to mass shootings, Anthony Edwards' acting debut, Jurassic World: Dominion, Geico getting sued for giving a woman an STD, and Robert DeNiro suggesting Zelensky should pull up to TriBeCa!
